==========
 segtools
==========
by Michael Hoffman <mmh1@washington.edu>
and Orion Buske <orion.buske@gmail.com>


Installation
============

Prerequisites to this installation guide:
    Python 2.5.1+
    Zlib
    R 2.7+ (compiled with --enable-R-shlib)
    The following R packages (installed in R with install.packages):
        lattice
        RColorBrewer
        latticeExtra

Installation has been simplified with the install.py script.

1) Download and run the install.py script:
   wget http://encodestatistics.org/svn/segmentation_validation/trunk/src/segtools/install.py
   python install.py